cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with generative modeling of 2D and 3D shapes, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and computer graphics (cs.GR). The use of deep neural networks and quantitative metrics for evaluation suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the part-based approach and combinatorial dimension of the generative process may also be relevant to neural networks (cs.NE).
